Will the Mets sweep this short two-game series, or will the Yankees salvage a split? Game 2 of the 2022 Subway Series Wednesday night follows what was an exciting opener, in which the Mets quickly responded to the Yankees’ pair of first-inning home runs and came away with a 6-3 win in front of a sellout crowd at Citi Field. Follow along with The Post’s live coverage of Wednesday’s game.